--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This role manages mytop.

mytop is a console-based tool for monitoring the threads and overall performance
of MySQL servers. The user interface is modeled after familiar top application.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: mytop
       mytop_state: 'install'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
     - role: mytop
       mytop_state: 'remove'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VARIABLES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ROLE
  mytop_state
    Specify predetermined 'mytop_state' variable (string).

    Install: 'true' | 'yes' | 'install'
    Remove : 'false' | 'no' | 'remove'
    Default: 'install'

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PACKAGES
  mytop: >= 1.6
    CentOS, RedHat, Gentoo

